  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Sequin.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You shake your body to a phantom beat as chakra shrouds you, the earth beneath you trembling in rhythm with your movements as you take on a temporary gigantic form, finishing your performance with a realm-shaking pose. All creatures within range that are on the ground, burrowing underneath the ground, or are on a wall must make a Strength saving throw as the world around you bends to your will, taking 9d8 earth damage and being knocked prone, as well as taking 4 ranks of Bruised on a failure while only taking half damage on a success. Creatures that are burrowing must make the save at disadvantage and take double damage. Additionally, the affected area is now considered to be difficult terrain. Finally, this jutsu can also be used to dig up constructs, items hiding within the ground. It can also be used to clear large amounts of ground at once.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above A-Rank, increase the cost by 3, the damage by 2d8, and the ranks of bruised by 1.</p>",
